degrees of what he's feeling right now.

146
00:09:09,007 --> 00:09:10,674
Shortness of breath.

147
00:09:11,426 --> 00:09:14,386
If he had worked
on those issues, there would be.

148
00:09:14,721 --> 00:09:17,306
